%% Diagram: Orchestrated saga with compensating transactions on failure
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client
    participant Orch as Saga Orchestrator
    participant Order as Order Service
    participant Pay as Payment Service
    participant Inv as Inventory Service
    participant Ship as Shipping Service

    Client->>Orch: place order

    Orch->>Order: create order (PENDING)
    Order-->>Orch: ok

    Orch->>Pay: reserve payment
    Pay-->>Orch: ok

    Orch->>Inv: reserve items
    Inv--xOrch: FAIL (out of stock)

    rect rgb(255, 232, 232)
    note over Orch,Ship: Compensate in reverse order\n(idempotent, semantic — not mechanical undo)
    Orch->>Pay: release payment hold
    Pay-->>Orch: ok
    Orch->>Order: cancel order
    Order-->>Orch: ok
    end

    Orch-->>Client: order failed,\ncompensations applied
